{"tid":2114030,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"旅行喼集中討論Post","createTime":"2020-07-18T13:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T00:49:57.000Z","uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ad974c330fa11eaa1e92a7e7ecb2f01fbfc30e","tid":2114030,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"見旅遊台一個旅行喼集中討論都冇所以開一個大家一齊討論下。雖然冇得去旅行不過都可以傾下有咩brand好用。<br />\n<br />\n我自己用過samsonite，delsey，ameriacan tourist，rimowa。覺得如果性價比最高係delsey，之前blackfriday買30寸都係1000蚊。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家入左rimowa坑，手上有<br />\nsalsa 30 x 1 <br />\ntopas 30 x 1 <br />\n黎緊應該入多個handcarry同30寸 ， 可能limbo handcarry加個classic 30寸。<br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得係overprice，同埋好易俾人掟爛，不過自己用過咁多次都冇事同埋真係超好推。有次裝咗差唔多四十kg一樣超級易推。同埋個型真係好好J。"},{"pid":"eb65f99f8a01176554aad4b634b9126529ebb1e0","tid":2114030,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"用開samsonite<br />\n夠硬淨耐用<br />\n好拉程度一般<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無又硬淨耐用又好拉的牌子介紹"},{"pid":"89d4d85325ab6a78d689410e7c9131f6575dde04","tid":2114030,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"用咗samsonite十年，1個32，1個28<br />\n<br />\n好實淨 好襟用 個轆都好好推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31efb2914b81edf3fb6c46884e92c3a546fd66e8","tid":2114030,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb65f99f8a01176554aad4b634b9126529ebb1e0","tid":2114030,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"用開samsonite<br />\n夠硬淨耐用<br />\n好拉程度一般<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無又硬淨耐用又好拉的牌子介紹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"真心叫我推一定係rimowa 前排轉新款勁抵買 <br />\n我諗samsonite都要2千幾？"},{"pid":"b8f0199594171fd45dd575a6a463fc2ffc15673a","tid":2114030,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p